SUBJECT: IMI- INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITIES IN UKRAINIAN
         DEFENSE CONVERSION: PIVDENNE (YUZHMASH)
         DESIGN BUREAU.


1. SUMMARY. FOLLOWING THE OPIC DEFENSE CONVERSION MISSION HELD IN UKRAINE IN
MARCH 1995, POST HAS RECEIVED A PACKAGE OF INVESTMENT AND JOINT VENTURE
PROPOSALS FROM THE PIVDENNE (RUSSIAN: YUZHMASH) RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT
BUREAU THAT PARTICIPATED IN THE MISSION. YUZHMASH IS ONE OF THE LARGEST
MISSILE AND SPACE CONGLOMERATES IN THE FORMER SOVIET UNION, AND ITS FORMER
DIRECTOR IS CURRENT UKRAINIAN PRESIDENT LEONID D. KUCHMA. THIS MESSAGE
PROVIDES A BRIEF OVERVIEW OF THE R&D BUREAU YUZHMASH AND DESCRIPTION OF ITS
DEFENSE CONVERSION PROJECTS. IN ADDITION, ALL PROJECTS LISTED HERE HAVE
PREPARED BUSINESS PLANS THAT CAN BE OBTAINED EITHER DIRECTLY FROM THE COMPANY
OR THROUGH USFCS KIEV. END SUMMARY. -------- OVERVIEW -------- 2. AS A
LEADING PART OF THE YUZHMASH ASSOCIATION, THE YUZHMASH R&D BUREAU IS A MAJOR
DEVELOPER OF SCIENCE-INTENSIVE TECHNOLOGIES. WITH A STAFF OF 5,000
HIGHLY-QUALIFIED RESEARCHERS, ENGINEERS, AND TECHNICIANS, THE COMPANY BOASTS
SIGNIFICANT SCIENTIFIC AND INTELLECTUAL POTENTIAL. YUZHMASH IS WHERE
UKRAINIAN PRESIDENT LEONID KUCHMA STARTED HIS SUCCESSFUL CAREER AS AN
ENGINEER AND LATER BECAME GENERAL DESIGNER AND DIRECTOR OF THE COMPANY.

3. THE COMPANY IS MOST ACTIVE IN MARKETING COMMERCIAL SPACE PRODUCTS AND
SERVICES, AND PROMOTING SPACE BOOSTERS AND SATELLITES. MILITARY PRODUCT LINES
INCLUDE: BALLISTIC MISSILES, MILITARY SATELLITES, AND SPACE BOOSTERS.
CIVILIAN PRODUCTION INCLUDES: THE ENERGIYA-BURAN SYSTEM; THE SL-16 ZENIT AND
SL-14 TSIKLON ROCKETS; OKEAN SATELLITES; SMALL RESEARCH SATELLITES; TRACTORS;
WIDE-BODY AIRPLANES; TROLLEY BUSES; PRODUCTS FOR THE AGROINDUSTRIAL COMPLEX;
VARIOUS CONSUMER GOODS. THE ENTERPRISE HAS, IN THE PAST, HAD ACCESS TO STATE
BUDGET FINANCING AND CREDITS FOR CONVERSION PROGRAMS. GIVEN THE DOWNTURN IN
MILITARY ORDERS AND LACK OF STATE FUNDING, MILITARY ENTERPRISES SUCH AS
YUZHMASH ARE SEEKING FOREIGN INVESTMENT TO CONVERT MILITARY PRODUCTION TO
CIVILIAN USE. REFTEL PROVIDED AN OVERVIEW OF UKRAINIAN DEFENSE CONVERSION
EFFORTS AS WELL AS INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITIES IN SIX SPECIFIC SECTORS.

