6.  A.  PROJECT NAME :  NAME OF THE PROJECT:
    DEVELOPMENT OF FIRE-PROTECTIVE MATERIALS
    BY UTILIZING ROCKET PROPELLANT-OXIDIZER.
B.  SECTOR: GENERAL INDUSTRIAL EQUIPMENT AND
    SUPPLIES
C.  ESTIMATED COST: $ 700,000
D.  PROJECT DESCRIPTION:  DISMANTLEMENT OF
    NUCLEAR WEAPONS IN UKRAINE REQUIRES UTILIZATION
    OF NUCLEAR COMPONENTS.  YUZHMASH CONDUCTED
    RESEARCH AND FOUND OUT THAT THE TREATMENT OF
    GRAPHITE WITH AN OXIDIZER PRODUCES A NEW
    MATERIAL, WHICH SIGNIFICANTLY INCREASES
    ITS VOLUME WITH AN INCREASE IN TEMPERATURE.
    THIS FEATURE CAN BE USED IN FIRE-EXTINGUISHERS
    AND FOR CREATION OF FIRE-RESISTANT POLYMERIC
    MATERIALS.  THE COMPANY EXPECTS A GREAT DEMAND
    FOR THIS MATERIAL IN UKRAINE AND OTHER NIS
    COUNTRIES.  YUZHMASH SEEKS A FOREIGN PARTNER
    TO LAUNCH PRODUCTION.

